# Testing

- Prefer Vitest contract/unit tests for `src/data` and `src/lib`.
- When changing projects/articles data, update co-located `*.test.ts`.
- When adding pure helpers, add tests in the same PR.
- Run `npm test` after data, routing, or schema changes.
- Do not add large page snapshots; keep tests high-signal for solo + agent maintenance.
- See `AGENTS.md` for the full pyramid and roadmap.
